			"subclassSource": "OathoftheWorkingClass",
			"subclassShortName": "Working Class",
			"level": 3,
			"entries": [
				"工人阶级的誓言完全致力于保护那些从事体力劳动职业或工业工作的人，他们无法保护自己不受社会链中高于他们的人的不平等待遇。",
				"当控制生产资料的人的行为变得卑劣时，反抗的火焰不断增长的人就会作为无产阶级的冠军出现，在《工人阶级誓言》下，他们煽动起义和反抗。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Tenets of the Working Class|Paladin||Working Class|OathoftheWorkingClass|3|OathoftheWorkingClass"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Oath Spells|Paladin||Working Class|OathoftheWorkingClass|3|OathoftheWorkingClass"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Channel Divinity|Paladin||Working Class|OathoftheWorkingClass|3|OathoftheWorkingClass"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Tenets of the Working Class",
			"source": "OathoftheWorkingClass",
			"className": "Paladin",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassSource": "OathoftheWorkingClass",
			"subclassShortName": "Working Class",
			"level": 3,
			"page": 1,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"工人阶级誓言的信条可能在强度和行动方式上有所不同，但都是围绕着与弱势群体并肩作战，反对那些愿意限制为他们工作的人的自由和生活条件的强权。它的中心原则很简单。",
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"entries": [
						{
							"type": "entries",
							"name": "Fight for Those Who Have to Work",
							"page": 1,
							"entries": [
								"在非人道的工作制度下，有许多人没有力量做任何事情，只能保持呼吸。你们是永远寻求保护这些人的堡垒。"
							]
						},
						{
							"type": "entries",
							"name": "No Mercy to the Profiteers",
							"page": 1,
							"entries": [
								"那些剥削我的战友的人不值得我怜悯，也不值得我尊敬。"
							]
						},
						{
							"type": "entries",
							"name": "Support for the Strikes",
							"page": 1,
							"entries": [
								"不要成为罢工者。你将永远支持反对拥有生产资料者的起义。"
							]
						},
						{
							"type": "entries",
							"name": "Make the Revolution",
							"page": 1,
							"entries": [
								"试图统治你和你的同志们的势力从不睡觉。你们的计划和行动必须始终以阶级斗争为目标。"
							]
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
